442247067db63ddbfaaef7de30c2fd9530d4b850, v78 (xcart_4_7_8), 2017-06-06 16:31:36, CHANGELOG, aim
------------------ X-CART v4.7.8 RELEASED

*DESIGN AND APPEARANCE*
[*] 13 Feb 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148318, B:0047576): Light responsive skin: Language selector is no longer shown in mobile menu if a single language is used. Thanks2Lehach.
[!] 28 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148361, B:0047783): [Product_Options] Options were displayed on one line in emails. Fixed.
[!] 16 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148352, B:0047723): Product line was cut in ideal_responsive for screens larger than 1280 px. Fixed.
[!] 15 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148330): ideal_responsive skin: Do not forget to enclose smarty params with '/". Fix for additional_class='responsive-row' in ideal_responsive skin.
[!] 07 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148342, B:0047688): Date selection calendar was overlapped by Flyout Menus in ideal_responsive skin. Fixed

*BACKOFFICE*
[*] 01 Jun 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148245): Country payment selector in the Admin area updated.
[*] 18 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148387): [Clean URLs] Added "RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/server-status" as instruction related to .htaccess file. Thanks to Abr.
[*] 04 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148367): Renamed the 'Real-time processors options' link to 'InterShipper options' on the ' Main page :: Shipping methods' page.
[*] 12 Feb 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148316, Y:0047563): In Admin area, list of categories and featured products jumped to bottom. Removed autofocus from skin/common_files/admin/main/featured_products.tpl. Thanks to Joe Funderburg (Cherie).
[!] 31 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148364, B:0046210): The test/live mode setting for Payflow Link now changes the mode for PayPal Express Checkout in accordance with the mode set for Payflow Link.
[!] 08 Feb 2017, mixon - Bug (Y:148312, B:0047542): The "Customer placed orders" link for anonymous customers was always showing zero orders on the profile modify page. Fixed.

*USERS*
[*] 16 Feb 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148326): Auto remove spaces before/after email on registration pages.
[!] 19 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148388, B:0047859): Profile Title selector was displayed incorrectly. Fixed. Thanks to Joe Funderburg (Cherie).
[!] 06 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148340): Pay With Amazon button did not appear sometimes, and console showed JavaScript error: uncaught typeerror (intermediate value).

*PRODUCTS*
[!] 25 May 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148405): 'Out of stock' message did not appear on the product details page without page reloading when Special_Offers module was disabled. Fixed. Thanks to Nogard.
[!] 06 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148372): Sometimes all products were renamed as restored_products if func_delete_product(0) was called in custom code. Fixed.
[!] 01 Feb 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148300, B:0047477): The products from the caregories that have just been enabled did not show up in the Customer area. Fixed.

*CATEGORIES*
[!] 17 Feb 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148327, B:0047604): If products are removed on the 'Categories management :: Category products' page, the Flyout Menus cache is removed.

*CART*
[*] 15 Feb 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148322): Added the expiry field for customer_saved_carts; default is SECONDS_PER_DAY*180.

*PAYMENTS*
[*] 19 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148389): [PayPal Standard] Use of HTTPS protocol is forced for PayPal Instant Payment Notifications if possible.
[*] 06 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148370): [PayPal Standard, Website Payments Pro Hosted, PayPal Express] Changed ipnpb.paypal.com to www.paypal.com following PayPal's strong recommendation.
[!] 18 May 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148401, B:0047974): [PayPal Payments Advanced] PayPal Payments Advanced did not use TEMPLATE=MOBILE on mobile devices. Fixed.
[!] 07 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148373): PayPal Standard rejected UK zips with spaces when address override checkbox was enabled. Fixed.

*SHIPPING*
[!] 02 Jun 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148413, B:0048040): Australia Post - PHP Fatal error for an international address on PHP5.3.x. Fixed.
[!] 26 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148392, B:0047900): The lowest cost shipping method was used as the default one. Fixed. Now the method that is first by position is used.
[!] 06 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148368): [USPS] error related to international locations and disabled 'Value of contents' setting. The element 'Package' has invalid child element 'Country'. List of possible elements expected: 'ValueOfContents'.

*CHECKOUT*
[!] 13 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148346): Just out of stock products are now handled correctly for Pay with Amazon (Amazon Pay) / Pilibaba Chinese Checkout / POS system / Bongo International for X-Cart.
[!] 13 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148345, B:0047706): Error "Cannot read property 'toUpperCase' of undefined JS error" on the One_Page_Checkout page (related to
countries without states). (TypeError: control.prop(...) is undefined). Fixed.

*ORDERS*
[*] 26 May 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148404, B:0047986): Added a new email notification: 'Order tracking info changed' notification to customer.
[*] 24 May 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148403, B:0047959): The error "No Google Maps API key provided. Please add ..." is no longer shown on the orders list. Thanks to Pino.
[!] 10 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148375, B:0047836): Products could be missing from orders sometimes when their quantity in stock was low.
[!] 10 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148343, B:0047703): Wrong text "Order status has been changed from Processed to Array" was displayed on the 'History of changes' popup in connection to the order 'Refund' status. Fixed.

*MODULES/ADD-ONS*
[*] 05 Jun 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148416): [MailChimp] Pre-built segments can now be used like "Recent Customers"/"First time customers"/"Repeat Customers"/"Lapsed Customers".
[*] 04 Jun 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148414): [Google Shopping] Added the ability not to send products for certain memberships to Google Shopping Feeds.
[*] 01 Jun 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148402): [ShippingEasy] module added. Thanks to Alex Zakharov.
[*] 31 May 2017, random - Improvement (Y:148410): [X-Payments Connector] and Antifraud updates: Security improvement. Allowed callback IP address for the connector can now be obtained from the Configuration bundle. PHP error when iframe was not enabled - Fixed. Saving a card from profile could result in a charge instead of authorization - Fixed. Address book was not editable from the Admin backend - Fixed. Checkout freeze when switching between shipping methods with the same cost - Fixed. When a recharge failed, the cart was messed up - Fixed. Fixed the notice when saving a card. Added support for API 1.7 - to get fraud check data.
[*] 29 May 2017, random - Improvement (Y:148407): [X-Payments Subscriptions] cumulative update (upgrade script required). Fixed the error causing an extra pending order to be created on Subscriptions cron execution. Now it is possible to use an existing saved card to pay for subscriptions. There is a new option to start subscriptions after an "Auth only" payment. Fixed error parsing for subscription payments. It is now possible to change the card used for a subscription. Anonymous customers are now required to log in before they can proceed with checkout.
[*] 25 May 2017, nikita - Improvement (Y:148406): CloudSearch: 1.3.8 Only embedded pages are indexed (root-level pages are excluded).
[*] 23 May 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148369): [Facebook_Ecommerce] Added Facebook feed and Facebook pixel integrations.
[*] 24 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148390, B:0047849): [Amazon Feeds] It is now possible to search by Amazon product type and to unset the Amazon product type.
[*] 18 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148313): Mandrill Integration added.
[*] 17 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148385, B:0047871): [Amazon Feeds] rejected - EAN is invalid. 'ISBN','UPC','EAN','ASIN','GTIN','GCID','PZN' can now be used as extra fields.
[*] 30 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148357, B:0047441): [Amazon feeds] It is now possible to send sale price (list price) and zero values.
[*] 29 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148363, B:0047441): [Amazon feeds] Added a new 'Product feed preferred description' setting that enables you to choose between short/detailed product description.
[*] 22 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148124, B:0047441): Amazon feeds: Updated Amazon product type categories.
[*] 20 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148354): [MailChimp] Added a new selector 'Link orders created outside campaigns to this store'. Leave this field blank to ensure that only orders created via a MailChimp campaign link are sent to MailChimp.
[*] 09 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148338 Y:148249): Amazon Pay: Authorizations that get declined are now handled with reason code InvalidPaymentMethod. Asynchronous Authorisation. An email is sent to customer to change payment method. [Amazon_Payments_Advanced]
[*] 02 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148331): Pay with Amazon: Renamed Pay with Amazon to Amazon Pay.
[*] 15 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148347, B:0047662): White screen (fatal error) on the 'Edit ordered products' page (related to Advanced Order Management and TaxCloud modules). Fixed.
[!] 12 May 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148400, B:0047919): [Amazon Feeds] Products from the 'Miscellaneous' category were not exported to Amazon. Fixed.
[!] 26 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148393, B:0047809): [Amazon Feeds] Amazon API returned no results. Fixed. Amazon Feeds can now be used with a UK / DE account.
[!] 17 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148383): [Pay with Amazon] Amazon Pay could be enabled when Amazon Feeds was used. Fixed.
[!] 17 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148384): [Amazon Feeds] products with variants were not passed when incremental export was used. Fixed.
[!] 14 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148382, B:0047861): [Amazon Feeds] was rejecting feeds as product images were image.php, not an actual image. Fixed.
[!] 27 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148360): [MailChimp] Sometimes orders/carts with just added products were not passed to MailChimp. Fixed.
[!] 26 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148359, B:0047777): [Product Options] The option 'Redirect a customer who clicks the "Buy Now" or "Add to wish list" buttons of a product with product options to product details page' did not work correctly for products with disabled product options. Fixed.
[!] 16 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148351): Dont_Miss_Out did not work with the setting 'Use new module initialization routine' disabled. Fixed.
[!] 01 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148335): Pay with Amazon did not work for Platinum edition if a cart contained products from different providers. Fixed.
[!] 27 Feb 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148332): [Bongo International] Error: "The following items are not available for export. Please remove the item(s) from your cart to proceed with your checkout." Fixed.
[!] 22 Feb 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148324): Link from Mailchimp Abandoned Cart Email was not working. Orders could not be assigned to a campaign. Orders had a wrong date. Ecommerce dashboard section was empty. Product's recommendations did not work. Fixed.
[!] 14 Feb 2017, mixon - Bug (Y:148238, B:0047139): Display price was changed on the Edit products page if tax was configured to be displayed in price.
[!] 06 Feb 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148305): Don't Miss Out: The alert is shown even for an out of stock product if the product is in the cart. The alert is not shown for the same user after her login. Performance optimization. [Dont_Miss_Out]
[!] 02 Feb 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148301, B:0047495): Don't Miss Out: SQL error. Fxed. Thanks to Isden. [Dont_Miss_Out]

*IMPORT/EXPORT*
[!] 12 Apr 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148377): The Pos. field was not set correctly sometimes during product import. Fixed.

*PERFORMANCE*
[*] 17 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148378, B:0047848): Import performance improvement for images. Imagick->unsharpMaskImage is used if possible instead of phpunsharpmask.php
[*] 14 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148380, B:0047867): Import performance improvement for when the 'Drop' checkbox option is enabled and the csv file contains the IMAGE column.
[*] 03 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148365): Special offers performance optimization. Thanks to Abr.
[*] 03 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148366): [Special offers] Added a new tool to decrease/optimize xcart_orders mysql table size on the admin/tools.php page (related to the 'Special offers applied' section on the order page).
[*] 15 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148348, B:0047631): Cache static content. Add commented content-type: application/javascript to .htaccess. Thanks to Seyfin.
[*] 13 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148344): Small optimization for Next/Previous order links.
[!] 21 Mar 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148355): Order Status change was working slowly if 'Custom Order Statuses' module was used. Fixed. [XOrder_Statuses]

*SECURITY*
[*] 10 Apr 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148374): IPv6 can now be used with the "User Access Control"/ADMIN_ALLOWED_IP features from config.php.

*MISCELLANEOUS*
[*] 01 Jun 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148376): [PHP 71 compatible] PHP7.1 critical bugfix related to strings and array operations.
[*] 01 Jun 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148376):  [PHP 71 compatible] Fix related to Special_Offers creation. PHP7.1 minor bugfix.
[*] 30 May 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148409, B:0047998): It is now possible to use special chars in the company name in the company emails (Site administrator, Users department, Orders department, Help/Support department and Company "From" addresses). The format is "Your Company Name1&Name2" sales@yourstore.com
[*] 24 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148220): [Google Analytics] Search phrases can now be tracked via Universal Google Analytics.
[*] 17 Mar 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148353): Updated PHPMailer version from 5.2.22 to 5.2.23 (Stores with the setting 'Use SMTP server instead of internal PHP mailer' enabled are affected).
[*] 13 Feb 2017, mixon - Improvement (Y:148319): Popup open: Added mobile device rotation support.
[*] 08 Feb 2017, mixon - Improvement (Y:148310): Amazon Feeds: Feeds API updated to 2016-09-21. Errors in PHP7 have been fixed.
[*] 08 Feb 2017, mixon - Improvement (Y:148309): Amazon Feeds: Sellers API updated.

------------------ X-CART v4.7.7 RELEASED

*DESIGN AND APPEARANCE*
[!] 27 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148199, B:0042326): Button bug using Chrome, Books & Magazine skin, zoom view. Ugly gap in button. Fixed.
[!] 19 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148187, B:0045289): Thumbnail image was not centered in the image box in some skins / screen resolutions. Fixed.
[!] 11 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148178, B:0046787): Minicart display issue in Ideal skins. Fixed.
[!] 03 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148156): Multi-currency: Top menu display issue on some screen resolutions in Light responsive skin. Fixed.
[!] 03 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148159): OPC: Light responsive "Checkout" and "Greetings,..." text was not centered on medium resolutions on the checkout page. Fixed.
[!] 30 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148153, S:0145717): FLC: Social Login & Fast Lane Checkout/checkout page layout was broken. Fixed.
[!] 26 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (S:0137693): Bill me later: With banner location specified as 'Near "Checkout with Bill Me Later" button', the button was not displayed in full. Fixed.
[!] 22 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148142, S:0137815): FLC: Personal details page display issues (not centered + whitespace). Fixed.
[!] 21 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148073, B:0046238): CSS was not loaded on the Products Map page in Ideal responsive skin.
[!] 06 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148115): Alternative checkout buttons: The buttons "Paypal Express" + "Pay with Amazon" were displayed incorrectly. Fixed.
[!] 26 Aug 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148061, B:0046243): Detailed Product Images & Light Responsive skin - display on Ipad / Iphone (within the body of the Product details page, colorbox, cloudzoom, internal popup). Fixed.

*BACKOFFICE*
[*] 20 Oct 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148191): Updated the http://SHOP_URL/check_requirements.php?checkrequirements=1&auth_code=<installation_auth_code>; tool to provide optimal X-Cart performance. Added a comment related to PHP7.
[*] 17 Aug 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148088): Changed the 'Error enabling module!' top message to 'Couldn't enable the module. Please check the file var/log/x-errors_php-<date>.php.'
[!] 20 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148221, B:0047072): Increased variant SKU textfield size on the 'Product management' -> 'Product variants ' page.
[!] 14 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148212, B:0047023): Product names were truncated to 30 symbols in the Bookmarks section in the 'Select a product' dialog. Changed to 72. Thanks to Ross Kelson.
[!] 14 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148213, B:0047024): Product names were truncated to 50 symbols on the product modify page. Changed to 72. Thanks to Ross Kelson.
[!] 28 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148200, B:0046901, S:0072214): If "USE_SQL_DATA_CACHE" was set to "true", Product quantity was cached, and the changes were not displayed in product search results list in the Admin back end. Fixed.
[!] 20 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148192, B:0046871): X-Cart news were not shown in the Admin area if its directory name was not the default one. Fixed.
[!] 15 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148184): Added a warning in the Admin area: "One or more static pages required for the correct display of hyperlinks in the phrase 'I accept the "Terms & Conditions" and "Privacy statement"' during One page checkout have been removed and are missing".
[!] 10 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148175): 'Test/demo data has been removed unsuccessfully.' error was shown when the 'Remove data' feature was used on the 'Main page :: Maintenance' page. Fixed.
[!] 07 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148170): Added a Dashboard notification related to when the option "Use new module initialization routine" is disabled.
[!] 09 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148079, B:0046308): Static page with special symbols did not show up on the static page modify page. Fixed.
[!] 21 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148068, B:0046288): Price without tax was displayed when 'Generated HTML Links' feature was used on the product modify page. Fixed.
[!] 11 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:51): Replaced the note 'You have marked all the possible product variants as exceptions. Now this product cannot be purchased.' with 'Make sure the product can still be purchased'. [Product option exceptions]

*USERS*
[!] 23 Jan 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148227): Logged-in users were not redirected to the requested page like Wishlist/address_book etc when 'Social Login'[XAuth] module was used. Fixed.
[!] 17 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148219): Small optimization for the 'Search for users' function. Thanks to Abr.
[!] 26 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148098): Reference to entity "utm_medium" for which no system identifier could be generated - w3c error related to X-Cart news. Fixed.
[!] 19 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148093, B:0046443): Call to undefined function func_get_default_fields() in include/search_users.php in the admin area when all the modules were disabled. Fixed. Thanks to Joe Funderburg (Cherie)
[!] 27 Jun 2016, aim - Bug (Y:27): Search-In checkboxes were unchecked by default on the 'Main page :: Users management' page. Fixed. https://forum.x-cart.com/showthread.php?t=74113

*CATEGORIES*
[!] 16 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148087, B:0046420): Flyout Menus: Membership categories were not shown when "Cache the menu" was on. Fixed.

*CART*
[!] 17 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148218): Trademark symbols were not shown in free shipping names (related to Special_Offers module). Fixed. [Special_Offers]

*PAYMENTS*
[*] 25 Jan 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148291): Force use https protocol for PayPal Instant Payment Notifications if possible.
[*] 13 Jul 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148054): Removed 'E-Gold' payment gateway support (obsolete). Thanks to Joliaj.
[!] 12 Jan 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148282, B:0047375): Pay with Amazon: Shipping destination zone was determined incorrectly for UK. Fixed.
[!] 17 Dec 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148257): Duplicate empty parameters are not passed to PayPal Payments Standard now.
[!] 12 Dec 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148239, B:0046949): PayPal: Added Payment Reversal and Cancel Reversal support.
[!] 16 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148216, B:0046840): Updated 'ANZ eGate - Bank-Hosted' (cc_anz.php) (Adaptation to the decommissioning of the MD5 hash algorithm 30 November 2016).
[!] 13 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148182, B:0046824): eWay - Responsive Shared Page: Error "Authentication Failure - the API credentials are incorrect" while processing payments via eWay. Fixed.
[!] 06 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148168, B:0046771): Virtual Merchant (Provided Form) payment gateway did not work when a long PIN was used. Fixed.
[!] 05 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148166, B:0046759, M:0125646): Removed PayPal Website Payments Standard "shopping_url" param to fix the problem with canceled orders.
[!] 21 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148141): PayPal Advanced "Cancel" button did not work on small screens. Fixed.
[!] 21 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148139, B:0043120, S:0134411): PayPal Express missing redirect on Declined Status (Error: This transaction couldn't be completed). Fixed.
[!] 17 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148063, B:0046281): 'Total has to be sub total plus value added tax plus shipping.' error related to the 'First Data Global Gateway - Connect 2.0' payment gateway and 'EMEA - Europe, the Middle East and Africa' region. Fixed.
[!] 04 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148058, B:0046262, B:0046322): Cart was sometimes not being cleared when an online payment gateway was used. Fixed. Thanks to Pavel Gavrilenko.
[!] 20 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:48, B:0046223): Payment method surcharge was not passed to PayPal. Fixed for PayPal Payments Standard/Website Payments Standard.
[!] 08 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:49): Switching the Test/Live mode setting for PayPal Payments Advanced on or off now changes the Test/Live mode setting for PayPal Express Checkout accordingly.

*SHIPPING*
[*] 14 Dec 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:148241, B:0047123): A rate returned by a real-time shipping processor can now be used as a base for a percentage markup field.
[*] 16 Jul 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:31): Added the ability to use 'Registered Post' service option for Australia Post. Added new methods: Australia Post Large Letter(125g)(250g)(500g) [APOST]
[!] 10 Jan 2017, mixon - Bug (Y:148278, B:0047365): Test real-time shipping rates calculation: The dimensions specified did not apply. Fixed.
[!] 06 Jan 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148273, B:0047348): DHL methods were not displayed when "Use InterShipper calculation service" was used. Fixed.
[!] 06 Jan 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148273 B:0047348 [!]: FedEx Ground was displayed instead of FedEx International Ground when "Use InterShipper calculation service" was used and shipping was supposed to be international. Fixed.
[!] 21 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148140, B:0046272): DHL: Account number was missing from the quote service request. Fixed. Thanks to Vjk.

*TAXES*
[*] 04 Jul 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:30): Added SOAP check on the Main page :: Taxes page https://forum.x-cart.com/showpost.php?p=397325&postcount=28 . Thanks to Joe Funderburg (Cherie).

*CHECKOUT*
[!] 14 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148214, B:0047000, B:0046967): Anonymous registration at checkout did not work in Safari/Firefox as autocomplete="off" did not work for the related hidden password field. The error was "Entered password is too long or do not match. One or more required fields are empty or contain invalid values." Fixed.
[!] 04 Oct 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148164, B:0046762): County name was not showing on the Fast Lane checkout page. Fixed.

*ORDERS*
[*] 18 Jan 2017, mixon - Improvement (Y:148238): Applied tax values are now displayed on a per product basis (as price is) on the "Order details" page for better clarity.
[*] 21 Nov 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148222, B:0047073): Added SKUs in tooltips for each order at /admin/orders.php?mode=search on the 'Orders management' page.
[!] 26 Dec 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148265): Emails were not sent when special symbols were used in the '"From" email address' setting on the ' Main page :: General settings :: Company' page. Fixed. Thanks to Abr.
[!] 20 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148185, B:0040519): The Gift Certificate "Remaining amount" was not reduced if order status was changed from Queued / Declined to Complete. Fixed.
[!] 25 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148076, B:0046315): Order info was not deleted fully. Fixed. Thanks to Steve Stoyanov (Cflsystems).
[!] 22 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148075, B:0046300): Google_Analytics/GA did not track ecommerce transactions in some cases. Fixed. Thanks to Steve Stoyanov (Cflsystems).
[!] 11 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148057): Non-digital PO number was not displayed in invoices. Fixed.
[!] 27 Jun 2016, aim - Bug (Y:28): "Error: An error occurred during the verification of the CSV file. Please check your CSV file and fix the problem, then try again." related to the "Import order tracking numbers" feature. Fixed.

*MODULES/ADD-ONS*
[*] 12 Jan 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148064): Special Offers: Optimization for func_bonus_check_product. Notices fixed. php arguments by reference removed. [Special_Offers]
[*] 25 Nov 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148224, B:0047089): Egoods: Added a new checkbox setting: 'Only signed-in users who bought this product should be able to use this link'.
[*] 09 Dec 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148240, B:0046110): XPDF now works on PHP7. Email attachments are displayed correctly on Apple iPad / iPhone.
[*] 02 Dec 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148236, B:0047074): Google Shopping export. The amount of characters for export is limited to Max 5000 characters per description, 70 per brand, 150 per title.
[*] 02 Dec 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148082): Updated MailChimp's API to version 3.0. Added support for Abandoned Cart workflow, Product Recommendations.
[*] 11 Oct 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:19): Added integration with segment.com. Segment is a powerful data aggregator, it tracks e-commerce events and sends this info to such apps as Mixpanel, Google Analytics, Localytics, RJ Metrics, SalesForce, HubSpot, Optimizely, Clicky and other data processing tools.
[*] 05 Oct 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148094, B:0046396): Klarna Payment Methods SDK/API updated to "klarna/php-xmlrpc 5.0" version [Klarna_Payments]. 'Date of birth is incorrect' error added for countries excluding DE/NL. 'SSN value is incorrect.' error changed to 'Date of birth is incorrect'. Thanks to Isden.
[*] 28 Sep 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:14): Pay with Amazon module updated. Thanks to Aim.
[*] 21 Sep 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148060): Added the module "Pilibaba Chinese Checkout".
[*] 07 Sep 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:14): Mobile rendering optimization for popups, "OPC", "Add to cart popup", "Multicurrency" in "Ideal" and "Light" responsive skins.
[*] 05 Sep 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148105, B:0046478): Added the ability to listen to 'products.lng.import', 'products.lng.delete', 'products.lng.insert' and 'products.lng.update' events.
[*] 01 Sep 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:148070): Add to cart popup: Removed duplicate module scripts in responsive skins. "Responsive" + "mobile view" logic moved to common script.
[*] 24 Aug 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148097, B:0046465): On Sale icon can now be displayed on the Manufacturers page [On_Sale]
[*] 13 Jul 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148053): All new coupons now have the "Expires" field (like "m-d-year 23:59"). Expired coupons are marked red. Added a new setting "Default offset for the 'Expires' date of new coupons (in days)" on the "Main page :: General settings :: Discount Coupons" page.
[!] 09 Jan 2017, mixon - Bug (Y:148247, B:0047077): EU Cookie Law: Duplicate IDs in HTML templates. Fixed. Thanks to Lehach.
[!] 09 Jan 2017, mixon - Bug (Y:148247, B:0047077): EU Cookie Law: Cookie settings were not updated in popup. Fixed.
[!] 21 Dec 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148260, B:0047280): Special Offers: The offer icon was shown for all products regardless of the "Apply special offers discounts" option value. Fixed.
[!] 15 Dec 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148253): MySQL error related to hexadecimal literals and XMultiCurrency: "You have an error in your SQL syntax; check the manual that corresponds to your MySQL server version for the right syntax to use near 'x'24050204858372f26d7'". Fixed.
[!] 08 Dec 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148238, B:0047139): AOM: When editing an order in AOM, on the Edit products page a product's display price changed on its own after updating the order products if the tax applied to the order had been configured with the setting "Display product price including tax" enabled.
[!] 05 Dec 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148234, B:0046996): AOM: Shipping cost was changed to zero if order was previously edited in AOM and products data was changed. Fixed.
[!] 17 Nov 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148217): Custom Order Statuses module did not allow to use an apostrophe in a custom order description. Fixed. [XOrder_Statuses]
[!] 19 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148189, B:0046848): AOM: Shipping name was not updated on Edit order totals in AOM. Fixed.
[!] 03 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148157): Simplify: The widget was over-sized on certain resolutions in OPC + CC input controls too small in certain skins. Fixed.
[!] 27 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148149, B:0046725): Amazon Feeds: Amazon feed caused an SQL error, feed failed. Fixed.
[!] 21 Sep 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148137, B:0046705): "Fatal error: Cannot redeclare class PasswordHash" error (related to Wordpress plugin). Fixed
[!] 21 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148101): Social login: The module did not work when the "username as login" scheme was used. Thanks2aim.
[!] 06 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148113): Add to cart popup: Alternative checkout buttons were misaligned in some skins. Fixed.
[!] 06 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148111, B:0046578): AOM: Payment method surcharge could not be removed from an order. Fixed.
[!] 05 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148065, B:0046286): Pay with Amazon: Place order button was available even when shipping was unavailable. Fixed.
[!] 05 Sep 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148105, B:0046478): 'Use cache' feature did not work for the Sitemap module. Fixed.
[!] 05 Sep 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148109, B:0046566): Pay with Amazon: Fatal error on books_and_magazines/common_files. Fixed.
[!] 02 Sep 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148107, B:0046536): The combination 'Special offer + Free shipping + Apply bonus to selected shipping methods only' sometimes did not work properly. [Special_Offers]
[!] 24 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148096): UPS address verification did not work on the checkout page when Image_Verification was used. Fixed. [UPS_OnLine_Tools, Address Validation OnLine Tool]
[!] 23 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148074, B:0046307): UPS address verification did not work on the checkout page. Fixed. [UPS_OnLine_Tools, Address Validation OnLine Tool]
[!] 19 Aug 2016, mixon - Bug (S:0148661): AOM: 'Get price' button returned an incorrect price due to incorrect customer info in AOM. Fixed.
[!] 18 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148090, B:0046434): Social Login: There was an incorrect redirect when required Additional fields were used. Fixed.
[!] 09 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148080, B:0046381): "Config field 'eid, secret' is not valid!" error related to unconfigured Klarna_Payments. Fixed.
[!] 25 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148078): Call to undefined function func_get_urlencoded_orderids() in amazon_checkout.php on line 226. Fixed. Thanks to Sergey Kochulimov.
[!] 21 Jul 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:35): AOM: The 'Title' field in address sections was not updated on the 'Customer info' edit page. Fixed.
[!] 19 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148066, B:0046247): Hidden free products were not displayed in the "Add products for special price" section. Fixed.
[!] 18 Jul 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148052, B:0046241): "Price for all" was incorrect for "Add all to cart" feature on the product page in the Special Offer section. Fixed.
[!] 16 Jun 2016, aim - Bug (Y:20, S:0148538): Special Offers: "Offer products for free" was lost after conditional products were removed from cart. Fixed. [Special_Offers]

