*MISCELLANEOUS*
[*] 17 Jan 2017, mixon - Improvement (Y:148238): AOM: Applied tax values are now displayed on a per product basis (as price is) on the 'Products edit' page in AOM for better clarity.
[*] 16 Jan 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:148070): JqueryUI: Updated the library and related code to the latest version 1.12.1.
[*] 13 Jan 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148284, B:0047399): HTTPS links in XML sitemap are now used, if possible. SEO improvement.
[*] 11 Jan 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148263): SMTP PHPMailer updated from 5.2.16 to 5.2.22 version (affects stores with the setting 'Use SMTP server instead of internal PHP mailer' enabled).
[*] 03 Jan 2017, aim - Improvement (Y:148270): Removed old BYR(974):Belarusian Ruble currency as obsolete.
[*] 14 Nov 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148211): X-Cart can now be used on non-standard ports like 8080 or 4433.
[*] 26 Oct 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:148197, B:0046321): Added the ability to specify Google Maps API key on the General configuration page. Other related changes.
[*] 19 Oct 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:148186): Improvement of the SOAP class logging functions.
[*] 08 Sep 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:14): BlockUI "Wait message" improvements related to the display of the message on small screens.
[*] 02 Sep 2016, aim - Improvement (Y:148108): memoryCaching can now be used for Cache_Lite. https://pear.php.net/manual/en/package.caching.cache-lite.cache-lite.cache-lite.php
[*] 19 Aug 2016, mixon - Improvement (Y:148086): The "Select2" jquery lib updated to v4.0.3.
[*] 17 Aug 2016, aim - Bug (Y:148089): Fatal error: "Class 'XC_EditorEntity' not found in include/product_modify.php on line 839" when the 'Use new module initialization routine' setting was disabled. Fixed.
[!] 12 Jan 2017, aim - Bug (Y:25): Clean URLs autogeneration did not work in some cases. Fixed. Thanks to Magos.
[!] 11 Jan 2017, mixon - Bug (Y:148280): Banner system: An image for banners could not be added in admin until the tab was switched back to 'Add image'. Fixed.
[!] 03 Jan 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148271, B:0047340): 'HTTP/1.0 500 Internal Server Error' is now sent instead of 200 OK when a critical error (like 'Cannot connect to MySQL server') occurs. Thanks to Abr.
[!] 04 Jan 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148169): PHP7.1 critical bugfix related to strings and array operations. Uncaught Error: [] operator not supported for strings. [PHP 71 compatible]
[!] 04 Jan 2017, aim - Bug (Y:148169): PHP7.0 non-critical changes. Unknown Error: Methods with the same name as their class will not be constructors in a future version of PHP.deprecated constructor include/lib/Services/Services_JSON/JSON.php. [PHP 7 compatible]
[!] 26 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148196, B:0046911): The "Reset filter" link was not working in form filters with date range selector. Fixed.
[!] 19 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148186, B:0046828): The VAT validation service was not working correctly for Greece VAT numbers issue. Fixed.
[!] 03 Oct 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148154): Uncaught TypeError: ajax.widgets.simplify.prototype.isAjaxCheckout is not a function. Uncaught TypeError: ajax.widgets.paypal_redirect.prototype.isAjaxCheckout is not a function. Fixed.
[!] 29 Aug 2016, mixon - Bug (Y:148065, B:0046286): Notice: Undefined variable current_carrier in include/cart_calculate_totals.php on line 131 (when Pay with Amazon is used).

------------------ X-CART v4.7.6 RELEASED

*DESIGN AND APPEARANCE*
[!] 22 Mar 2016, mixon - Bug (0146039): HTML tags were displayed for currency values in plain text emails. Fixed.
