[*] 23 Apr 2014, mixon - Improvement (0139164): Minor improvements related to XAuth module init procedure.
[*] 22 Apr 2014, mixon - Improvement (0138944): Performance optimization: func_is_valid_ip, multiple call of the same function (trim) is replaced with
value.
[*] 21 Apr 2014, mixon - Improvement (0139356): Replaced font tag with span in the Customer front end.
