[*] 18 Jan 2013, aim - Improvement (0128449): Smarty security mode is now enabled. Changed smarty->secure_dir to skin folder.
[*] 15 Jan 2013, aim - Improvement (0129408): Refactoring for the include/admin_security.php file. Changed the file to func_check_admin_security_redirect() function.
