[!] 07 Sep 2012, abr - Bug (0125915): There was a syntax error in customer/main/product_details.tpl. Fixed.
[!] 28 Aug 2012, abr - Bug (0125632): PHP notices were generated during benchmark run as a result of attempts to access uninitialized elements of an array. Fixed.
[!] 22 Aug 2012, abr - Bug (0125482): The description for the func_print_d() function was misleading. Corrected.
[!] 22 Aug 2012, abr - Bug (0125462): There was no explicit "encoding" argument for htmlentities() and htmlspecialchars() functions. Fixed.
[!] 22 Aug 2012, abr - Bug (0125430): Disabling Product Options module caused a PHP notice on product pages. Fixed.
